On the earlier models they had hose that ran from the tank all the way 
to the filter (and as well from the regulator back to the tank).  On the 
later models, sections of that hose was replaced with steel pipe as you 
can see here:


76:
http://www.ratwell.com/technical/FuelHoses/FI_Kit_Inst_76.jpg

77:
http://www.ratwell.com/technical/FuelHoses/FI_Kit_Inst_77.jpg

78/79:
http://www.ratwell.com/technical/FuelHoses/FI_Kit_Inst_7879.jpg
